{"id":22737,"date":"2019-05-22T12:56:50","date_gmt":"2019-05-22T07:26:50","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/?p=22737"},"modified":"2023-11-22T17:41:45","modified_gmt":"2023-11-22T12:11:45","slug":"anurag-kashyap","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/anurag-kashyap\/","title":{"rendered":"Anurag Kashyap Wiki, Age, Girlfriend, Wife, Children, Family, Biography &amp; More"},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-22738\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap.jpg\" alt=\"Anurag Kashyap\" width=\"474\" height=\"345\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap.jpg 640w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-300x218.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 474px) 100vw, 474px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>Anurag Kashyap is a famous Indian film-maker. He is a recipient of several National and Filmfare awards. Starting his career as a co-writer in Ram Gopal Verma&#8217;s crime drama, Satya (1998), Kashyap achieved his breakthrough from Dev.D (2009). Due to his contribution to films and cinema, the government of France awarded him\u00a0the\u00a0Ordre des Arts et des Lettres\u00a0(Knight of the Order of\u00a0Arts and letters) in 2013.<\/p>\n<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_62 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-custom ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">Contents<\/p>\n<label for=\"ez-toc-cssicon-toggle-item-65bce5c15be91\" class=\"ez-toc-cssicon-toggle-label\"><span class=\"\"><span class=\"eztoc-hide\" style=\"display:none;\">Toggle<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-icon-toggle-span\"><svg style=\"fill: #000000;color:#000000\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #000000;color:#000000\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/span><\/label><input type=\"checkbox\"  id=\"ez-toc-cssicon-toggle-item-65bce5c15be91\"  aria-label=\"Toggle\" \/><nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 ' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/anurag-kashyap\/#WikiBiography\" title=\"Wiki\/Biography\">Wiki\/Biography<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/anurag-kashyap\/#Physical_Appearance\" title=\"Physical Appearance\">Physical Appearance<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/anurag-kashyap\/#Family\" title=\"Family\">Family<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/anurag-kashyap\/#Career\" title=\"Career\">Career<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/anurag-kashyap\/#Controversies\" title=\"Controversies\">Controversies<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/anurag-kashyap\/#AwardsHonours\" title=\"Awards\/Honours\">Awards\/Honours<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/anurag-kashyap\/#Favourite_Things\" title=\"Favourite Things\">Favourite Things<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/anurag-kashyap\/#Net_Worth\" title=\"Net Worth\">Net Worth<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-9\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/anurag-kashyap\/#Facts\" title=\"Facts\">Facts<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"WikiBiography\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080;\">Wiki\/Biography<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Anurag Kashyap was born on 10 September 1972 (<strong>Age: 48 years old, as of 2020<\/strong>) in Gorakhpur, Uttar Pradesh, India. His father, Prakash Singh was a Chief Engineer of Uttar Pradesh Power Corporation Limited. Kashyap received his primary education from Green School, Dehradun. When she was 8 years old, he was admitted to Scindia School in Gwalior.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_22752\" style=\"width: 292px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Childhood-photo-of-Anurag-Kashyap.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-22752\" class=\" wp-image-22752\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Childhood-photo-of-Anurag-Kashyap.jpg\" alt=\"Childhood photo of Anurag Kashyap\" width=\"282\" height=\"539\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Childhood-photo-of-Anurag-Kashyap.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Childhood-photo-of-Anurag-Kashyap-157x300.jpg 157w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 282px) 100vw, 282px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-22752\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Childhood photo of Anurag Kashyap<\/p><\/div>\n<p>He wanted to become a scientist. To pursue his dream of becoming a scientist, he enrolled at Hans Raj College in the University of Delhi. He completed his graduation in 1993 with a degree in Zoology. After graduation, he did many street plays. In 1993, he arrived in Mumbai with Rs. 5000 in the pocket. When the whole money spent, he passed several days on the streets and slept on beaches. Sometimes, he stayed at St. Xavier&#8217;s boys&#8217; hostel. Somehow, he managed to find works at Prithvi Theatre but his first play remained incomplete due to the death of the director.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Physical_Appearance\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080;\">Physical Appearance<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Height (approx.):<\/strong> 178 cm or 5&#8217;11&#8221;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Eye Colour:<\/strong> Black<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Hair Colour:<\/strong> Black<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-photo.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-22811\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-photo.jpg\" alt=\"Anurag Kashyap\" width=\"453\" height=\"575\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-photo.jpg 453w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-photo-236x300.jpg 236w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 453px) 100vw, 453px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Family\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080;\">Family<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Anurag Kashyap was born to Prakash Singh.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_22814\" style=\"width: 490px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-with-his-father.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-22814\" class=\"size-full wp-image-22814\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-with-his-father.jpg\" alt=\"Anurag Kashyap with his father\" width=\"480\" height=\"480\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-with-his-father.jpg 480w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-with-his-father-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-with-his-father-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-with-his-father-65x65.jpg 65w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 480px) 100vw, 480px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-22814\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Anurag Kashyap with his father<\/p><\/div>\n<p>He has one brother,\u00a0Abhinav Kashyap who is also a film director and screenwriter.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_22815\" style=\"width: 610px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-with-his-brother.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-22815\" class=\"size-full wp-image-22815\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-with-his-brother.jpg\" alt=\"Anurag Kashyap with his brother\" width=\"600\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-with-his-brother.jpg 600w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-with-his-brother-300x150.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-22815\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Anurag Kashyap with his brother<\/p><\/div>\n<p>Anubhuti Kashyap is his sister who also assists in most of his films.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_22816\" style=\"width: 518px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Sister-of-Anurag-Kashyap.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-22816\" class=\"size-full wp-image-22816\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Sister-of-Anurag-Kashyap.jpg\" alt=\"Sister of Anurag Kashyap\" width=\"508\" height=\"383\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Sister-of-Anurag-Kashyap.jpg 508w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Sister-of-Anurag-Kashyap-300x226.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 508px) 100vw, 508px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-22816\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sister of Anurag Kashyap<\/p><\/div>\n<p>He married Aarti Bajaj in 2003, she was his friend from early times. She is a film-editor and works in his films.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_22818\" style=\"width: 393px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-with-his-ex-wife-Aarti-Bajaj.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-22818\" class=\"size-full wp-image-22818\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-with-his-ex-wife-Aarti-Bajaj.jpg\" alt=\"Anurag Kashyap with his ex-wife, Aarti Bajaj\" width=\"383\" height=\"382\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-with-his-ex-wife-Aarti-Bajaj.jpg 383w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-with-his-ex-wife-Aarti-Bajaj-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-with-his-ex-wife-Aarti-Bajaj-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-with-his-ex-wife-Aarti-Bajaj-65x65.jpg 65w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 383px) 100vw, 383px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-22818\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Anurag Kashyap with his ex-wife, Aarti Bajaj<\/p><\/div>\n<p>The couple has a daughter,\u00a0Aaliya Kashyap. The couple divorced in 2009.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_22819\" style=\"width: 360px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-with-his-daughter.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-22819\" class=\"size-full wp-image-22819\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-with-his-daughter.jpg\" alt=\"Anurag Kashyap with his daughter\" width=\"350\" height=\"329\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-with-his-daughter.jpg 350w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-with-his-daughter-300x282.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 350px) 100vw, 350px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-22819\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Anurag Kashyap with his daughter<\/p><\/div>\n<p>After being divorced from his first wife, Anurag married actress, <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/kalki-koechlin\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Kalki Koechlin<\/a> in 2011. But, soon they got divorced in 2015.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_22821\" style=\"width: 640px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-and-Kalki-Koechlin.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-22821\" class=\"size-full wp-image-22821\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-and-Kalki-Koechlin.jpg\" alt=\"Anurag Kashyap and Kalki Koechlin\" width=\"630\" height=\"420\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-and-Kalki-Koechlin.jpg 630w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-and-Kalki-Koechlin-300x200.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-22821\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Anurag Kashyap and Kalki Koechlin<\/p><\/div>\n<p>He has an affair with Shubhra Shetty who works in media production.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_22822\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-with-his-girlfriend.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-22822\" class=\"size-full wp-image-22822\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-with-his-girlfriend.jpg\" alt=\"Anurag Kashyap with his girlfriend\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-with-his-girlfriend.jpg 500w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-with-his-girlfriend-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-with-his-girlfriend-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-with-his-girlfriend-65x65.jpg 65w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-22822\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Anurag Kashyap with his girlfriend<\/p><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Career\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080;\">Career<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>In 1995, he met a person named Pankaj Titoria by chance. Pankaj Titoria introduced him to film director and editor, Shivam Nair. At Shivam Nair&#8217;s home, Kashyap watched &#8216;Taxi Driver&#8217; and got enchanted with the film. In 1997, he wrote the screenplay of the first film of Hansal Mehta&#8217;s first film, &#8216;Jayate&#8217; which could not be released in the theater. In 1998, actor, Manoj Bajpayee suggested his name to the director, Ram Gopal Verma to write a film.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_22831\" style=\"width: 650px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-and-Manoj-Bajpayee.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-22831\" class=\"size-full wp-image-22831\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-and-Manoj-Bajpayee.jpg\" alt=\"Anurag Kashyap and Manoj Bajpayee\" width=\"640\" height=\"425\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-and-Manoj-Bajpayee.jpg 640w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-and-Manoj-Bajpayee-300x200.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-22831\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Anurag Kashyap and Manoj Bajpayee<\/p><\/div>\n<p>Ram Gopal Verma hired him after being impressed by his work of &#8216;Auto Narayan.&#8217; At that time, he wrote the script of &#8216;Satya&#8217; along with Saurabh Shukla. Satya was a successful film and it is regarded as one of the best films in the Indian Cinema. In 1999, he also wrote the script of &#8216;Kaun&#8217; and wrote the dialogues for &#8216;Shool.&#8217; The same year, he made a short film, &#8216;Last Train to Mahakali&#8217; for Television.<\/p>\n<div class=\"flex-video flex-video-youtube\"><iframe title=\"Last train to Mahakali - Part 1\" width=\"1060\" height=\"795\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/PVif5fCxzwg?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe><\/div>\n<p>Kashyap made his directorial debut in 2002 from the film, &#8216;<strong>Paanch<\/strong>.&#8217; The film was related to\u00a0Joshi-Abhyankar serial murders that took place in 1976. Initially, the film faced trouble with the Central Board of Film Certification. Meanwhile, Kashyap wrote the dialogues for many films such as Paisa Vasool\u00a0(2004), Yuva\u00a0(2004), a Canadian film, Water (2005), Main Aisa Hi Hoon (2005), etc. However, later, the film, &#8216;Paanch&#8217; was cleared by the board and was released in 2002 in many film festivals. In 2007, he worked on film &#8216;Black Friday&#8217; which was based on\u00a0Hussain Zaidi&#8217;s book with the same name and was related to the 1993 Bombay Bombings. However, the Bombay High Court put a stay on its release until the judgment in the bomb blast case was made. The same year, he made a remake of\u00a0Stephen King&#8217;s short story &#8220;Quitters&#8221; as &#8216;No Smoking.&#8217; In 2009, he founded his own production company, <strong>Anurag Kashyap Films<\/strong>. He made his debut in production from a critical hit, &#8216;Udaan.&#8217; Kashyap has also produced many films including\u00a0Shaitan\u00a0(2011), Chittagong\u00a0(2012),\u00a0Aiyyaa\u00a0(2012), etc. In 2011, he directed and co-wrote &#8216;That Girl in Yellow Boots&#8217; with <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/kalki-koechlin\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Kalki Koechlin<\/a>. The film was screened at many international film festivals. A famous American film critic,\u00a0Roger Ebert gave the film 3.5 stars out of 4. In 2012, Kashyap&#8217;s film Gangs of Wasseypur did the rounds and screened at 2012 Cannes\u00a0Directors&#8217; Fortnight, London Indian Film Festival, and Toronto Film Festival.<\/p>\n<div class=\"flex-video flex-video-youtube\"><iframe title=\"Gangs of Wasseypur Trailer\" width=\"1060\" height=\"596\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/j-AkWDkXcMY?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe><\/div>\n<p>In 2016, Kashyap directed Raman Raghav 2.0 starring <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/nawazuddin-siddiqui\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Nawazuddin Siddiqui<\/a> which met with a positive response. In 2018, he worked on &#8216;Lust Stories&#8217; collaborating with fellow directors,\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/zoya-akhtar\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Zoya Akhtar<\/a>,\u00a0Dibakar Banerjee, and <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/karan-johar\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Karan Johar<\/a>. On 15 June 2018, the film was released on Netflix.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Lust-Stories-poster.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-23743\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Lust-Stories-poster.jpg\" alt=\"Lust Stories poster\" width=\"426\" height=\"597\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Lust-Stories-poster.jpg 426w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Lust-Stories-poster-214x300.jpg 214w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 426px) 100vw, 426px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>Anurag Kashyap has also been a good actor and made his cameo appearances in many films including Black Friday (2007), Tera Kya Hoga Johnny, Dev.D, Gulaal, Bhoothnath Returns, Happy New Year, etc. In 2010, he played the role of a Police Officer in the film &#8216;Encounter.&#8217; In 2011, he became a villain in Tigmanshu Dhulia&#8217;s film &#8216;Shagird.&#8217; In 2016, he played the role of a corrupt police officer in\u00a0AR Murugadoss&#8217;s &#8216;Akira.&#8217; In 2018, he also acted in a Tamil film Imaikkaa Nodigal.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Controversies\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080;\">Controversies<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>In 2000, his directorial debut film, &#8216;Paanch&#8217; fell into controversies for the violent portrayal of youths.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>He is often criticized by media for promoting sex, drugs, abuses in his films.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>He produced the 2016 film &#8216;Udta Punjab&#8217; along with other producers. The film was criticized by the Censor Board for portraying Punjab in smoking and drugs.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>On 19 September 2020, Bollywood actress <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/payal-ghosh\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Payal Ghosh<\/a> took to Twitter to accuse Anurag Kashyap of sexual assault in the series of #MeToo campaign. In her tweet, she requested the Prime Minister of India Narendra Modi to take action in the matter. She also named a few Bollywood actresses like <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/huma-qureshi\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Huma Qureshi<\/a> and <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/richa-chadda\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Richa Chadda<\/a> and said they had also been the victim of sexual assault by Kashyap.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/anuragkashyap72?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">@anuragkashyap72<\/a> has forced himself on me and extremely badly. <a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/PMOIndia?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">@PMOIndia<\/a> <a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/narendramodi?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">@narendramodi<\/a> ji, kindly take action and let the country see the demon behind this creative guy. I am aware that it can harm me and my security is at risk. Pls help! <a href=\"https:\/\/t.co\/1q6BYsZpyx\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">https:\/\/t.co\/1q6BYsZpyx<\/a><\/p>\n<p>&mdash; Payal Ghosh\u0950 (@iampayalghosh) <a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/iampayalghosh\/status\/1307307613248462848?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">September 19, 2020<\/a><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https:\/\/platform.twitter.com\/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"><\/script><\/p>\n<p>After Payal Ghosh&#8217;s tweet, the chairperson of the National Commission for Women in India, Rekha Sharma, asked her to give details about the incident through her Twitter account.<\/p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Thank you will do that \ud83d\ude4f\ud83c\udffc <a href=\"https:\/\/t.co\/xQVgzIh0cU\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">https:\/\/t.co\/xQVgzIh0cU<\/a><\/p>\n<p>&mdash; Payal Ghosh\u0950 (@iampayalghosh) <a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/iampayalghosh\/status\/1307341906561519616?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">September 19, 2020<\/a><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https:\/\/platform.twitter.com\/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"><\/script><\/p>\n<p>Bolywwod actress <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/kangana-ranaut\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Kangana Ranaut<\/a> also took to Twitter to support Payal Ghosh.<\/p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Bullywood is full of sexual predators who have fake and dummy marriages they expect a new hot young girl to make them happy everyday, they do the same to young vulnerable men also,I have settled my scores my way I don\u2019t need <a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/hashtag\/MeToo?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">#MeToo<\/a> but most girls do <a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/hashtag\/PayalGhosh?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">#PayalGhosh<\/a> <a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/hashtag\/AnuragKashyap?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">#AnuragKashyap<\/a><\/p>\n<p>&mdash; Kangana Ranaut (@KanganaTeam) <a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/KanganaTeam\/status\/1307602444973531136?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">September 20, 2020<\/a><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https:\/\/platform.twitter.com\/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"><\/script><\/p>\n<p>Anurag Kashyap refuted these claims through a series of tweets.<\/p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"hi\" dir=\"ltr\">\u0915\u094d\u092f\u093e \u092c\u093e\u0924 \u0939\u0948 , \u0907\u0924\u0928\u093e \u0938\u092e\u092f \u0932\u0947 \u0932\u093f\u092f\u093e \u092e\u0941\u091d\u0947 \u091a\u0941\u092a \u0915\u0930\u0935\u093e\u0928\u0947 \u0915\u0940 \u0915\u094b\u0936\u093f\u0936 \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u0964 \u091a\u0932\u094b \u0915\u094b\u0908 \u0928\u0939\u0940\u0902 \u0964\u092e\u0941\u091d\u0947 \u091a\u0941\u092a \u0915\u0930\u093e\u0924\u0947 \u0915\u0930\u093e\u0924\u0947 \u0907\u0924\u0928\u093e \u091d\u0942\u0920 \u092c\u094b\u0932 \u0917\u090f \u0915\u0940 \u0914\u0930\u0924 \u0939\u094b\u0924\u0947 \u0939\u0941\u090f \u0926\u0942\u0938\u0930\u0940 \u0914\u0930\u0924\u094b\u0902 \u0915\u094b \u092d\u0940 \u0938\u0902\u0917 \u0918\u0938\u0940\u091f \u0932\u093f\u092f\u093e\u0964 \u0925\u094b\u0921\u093c\u0940 \u0924\u094b \u092e\u0930\u094d\u092f\u093e\u0926\u093e \u0930\u0916\u093f\u090f \u092e\u0948\u0921\u092e\u0964 \u092c\u0938 \u092f\u0939\u0940 \u0915\u0939\u0942\u0901\u0917\u093e \u0915\u0940 \u091c\u094b \u092d\u0940 \u0906\u0930\u094b\u092a \u0939\u0948\u0902 \u0906\u092a\u0915\u0947 \u0938\u092c \u092c\u0947\u092c\u0941\u0928\u093f\u092f\u093e\u0926 \u0939\u0948\u0902 \u0964\u0967\/\u096a<\/p>\n<p>&mdash; Anurag Kashyap (@anuragkashyap72) <a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/anuragkashyap72\/status\/1307396141105913856?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">September 19, 2020<\/a><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https:\/\/platform.twitter.com\/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"><\/script><\/p>\n<p>On 21 September 2020, he released his lawyer&#8217;s statement and resolved to pursue the matter legally.<\/p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">And here is the statement from my lawyer <a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/PriyankaKhimani?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">@PriyankaKhimani<\/a> .. on my behalf .. thank You <a href=\"https:\/\/t.co\/0eXwNnK5ZI\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">pic.twitter.com\/0eXwNnK5ZI<\/a><\/p>\n<p>&mdash; Anurag Kashyap (@anuragkashyap72) <a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/anuragkashyap72\/status\/1307755676051992576?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">September 20, 2020<\/a><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https:\/\/platform.twitter.com\/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"><\/script><\/p>\n<p>On 23 September, Payal Ghosh lodged an FIR against Anurag at the Versova police station in Mumbai. In the FIR, she accused Mr. Kashyap of raping her at a place on Yari Road in Versova in 2013. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_22737_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_22737_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_22737_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_22737_1_1\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[1]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_22737_1_1\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ndtv.com\/india-news\/actor-files-rape-case-against-filmmaker-anurag-kashyap-2299844\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">NDTV<\/a><\/span><\/span> In August 2023, she discussed the matter and expressed that she was confronting Kashyap\u2019s influence in the industry on her own, noting that few are willing to speak out against him. She said,<\/p>\n<blockquote><p>I am not the richest or the most powerful and so I don\u2019t even expect others to come out and support me against him. I am fighting the battle alone and I know that\u2019s how it is going to be in future as well. Nobody will take a stand for me and go against him. Everyone values their relations with him because he is a film director.\u201d <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_22737_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_22737_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_22737_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_22737_1_2\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[2]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_22737_1_2\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/www.freepressjournal.in\/entertainment\/payal-ghosh-on-her-sexual-harassment-claims-against-anurag-kashyap-everyone-values-their-relations-with-him-as-he-is-a-filmmaker\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">The Free Press Journal<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>In March 2021, the Income Tax department found the discrepancy and manipulation in income worth Rs. 650 crore after raids on Anurag Kashyap, <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/taapsee-pannu\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Taapsee Pannu<\/a>, and Vikas Bahl. The raids were part of a tax evasion probe against Phantom Films, which were carried out across 30 locations in Mumbai and Pune on 3 March 2021. According to the I-T dept. officials, the production house staff was not able to explain the discrepancy of around Rs. 300 crore; moreover, manipulation and under-valuation of share transactions of Phantom Films amongst the film directors and shareholders, having tax implication of about Rs. 350 crores, were also quoted by the officials, and the evidence of cash receipts by the leading actress amounting to Rs. 5 crores was also recovered. Opposition parties slammed the raids and termed these raids as the Modi government&#8217;s vengeance against those who spoke against the government and supported the ongoing farmer&#8217;s protest. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_22737_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_22737_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_22737_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_22737_1_3\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[3]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_22737_1_3\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/www.hindustantimes.com\/cities\/mumbai-news\/found-discrepancy-manipulation-in-income-worth-rs-650-crore-says-i-t-dept-after-raids-on-anurag-kashyap-taapsee-pannu-101614862392768.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">Hindustan Times<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"AwardsHonours\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080;\">Awards\/Honours<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Screen Award for Best Screenplay with\u00a0Saurabh Shukla\u00a0for\u00a0Satya (1999)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Special Jury Award for Last Train to Mahakali (2000)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Grand Jury Prize for Black Friday (2007)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Best Story\u00a0and\u00a0Best Screenplay\u00a0Award along with\u00a0Vikramaditya Motwane (2011)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Ordre des Arts et des Lettres\u00a0(Knight of the Order of Arts and Letters) by the\u00a0government of France (2013)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Yash Bharti Award\u00a0by the\u00a0Government of Uttar Pradesh (2016)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Favourite_Things\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080;\">Favourite Things<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Food(s):<\/strong> Cheese, Cereals, Fish, Chocolate, Nespresso<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Film(s):<\/strong> Bicycle Thieves, Pyasa, Bandit Queen, Sahib Biwi Aur Gulam<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Actor(s):<\/strong> Dilip Kumar, <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/amitabh-bachchan\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Amitabh Bachchan<\/a>,\u00a0Naseeruddin Shah<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Actresses:<\/strong>\u00a0Marilyn Monroe,\u00a0Golshifteh Farahani,\u00a0Scarlett Johansson<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Net_Worth\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080;\">Net Worth<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>As in 2018, his net worth is around $110 million.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Facts\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080;\">Facts<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>He likes to smoke and drink.\n<div id=\"attachment_23781\" style=\"width: 355px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-smokes-1.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-23781\" class=\" wp-image-23781\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-smokes-1.jpg\" alt=\"Anurag Kashyap smokes\" width=\"345\" height=\"345\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-smokes-1.jpg 480w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-smokes-1-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-smokes-1-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-smokes-1-65x65.jpg 65w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 345px) 100vw, 345px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-23781\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Anurag Kashyap smokes<\/p><\/div>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_23782\" style=\"width: 471px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-drinks-alcohol.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-23782\" class=\" wp-image-23782\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-drinks-alcohol.jpg\" alt=\"Anurag Kashyap drinks alcohol\" width=\"461\" height=\"346\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-drinks-alcohol.jpg 640w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-drinks-alcohol-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 461px) 100vw, 461px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-23782\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Anurag Kashyap drinks alcohol<\/p><\/div><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>After completing his graduation in 1993, he joined a street theatre group &#8220;Jana Natya Manch.&#8221; The same year, he attended the International Film Festival and watched 55 films in 10 days.\u00a0Vittorio De Sica&#8217;s &#8216;Bicycle Thieves&#8217; influenced him most.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>He is regarded as an auteur and credited for pioneering India&#8217;s Indie scenes in the early 2000s.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Filmmaker, <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/zoya-akhtar\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Zoya Akhtar<\/a> has written about him, &#8220;He has a very strong storytelling style and he proved that you could tell a great story with not a lot of money.&#8221;\n<p><div id=\"attachment_23788\" style=\"width: 599px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-with-Zoya-Akhtar-Karan-Johar-and-Dibakar-Banerjee.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-23788\" class=\" wp-image-23788\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-with-Zoya-Akhtar-Karan-Johar-and-Dibakar-Banerjee.jpg\" alt=\"Anurag Kashyap with Zoya Akhtar, Karan Johar and Dibakar Banerjee\" width=\"589\" height=\"325\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-with-Zoya-Akhtar-Karan-Johar-and-Dibakar-Banerjee.jpg 694w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Anurag-Kashyap-with-Zoya-Akhtar-Karan-Johar-and-Dibakar-Banerjee-300x166.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 589px) 100vw, 589px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-23788\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Anurag Kashyap with Zoya Akhtar, Karan Johar, and Dibakar Banerjee<\/p><\/div><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>A Canadian critic, Cameron Bailey has called Kashyap\u00a0&#8220;one of the most knowledgeable filmmakers.&#8221;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>The British director,\u00a0Danny Boyle has praised Kashyap&#8217;s work in direction and copied the filmmaking style of Kashyap in some of the scenes in Oscar Winning movie,\u00a0<strong>Slumdog Millionaire<\/strong>.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>He does not believe in religion. According to him, &#8220;I am an Athiest.\u00a0Cinema is the only religion i believe in.&#8221;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Kashyap is a member of the board of the\u00a0NGO, <strong>Aangan<\/strong>, which helps protect vulnerable children around India.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>His hobbies are writing, swimming, listening to music, etc.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Anurag Kashyap once, in an interview, talked about the making of the series &#8216;Maximum City,&#8217; an adaptation of writer Suketu Mehta\u2019s book of the same name. He revealed that when Netflix decided to shelve his project, the stress took a toll on him which led him to find solace in alcohol and experience depression. He, moreover, mentioned that suffered two heart attacks at that time. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_22737_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_22737_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_22737_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_22737_1_4\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[4]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_22737_1_4\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/indianexpress.com\/article\/entertainment\/bollywood\/anurag-kashyap-depression-drank-heavily-two-heart-attacks-after-netflix-walked-out-of-maximum-city-9036064\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">The Indian Express<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div class=\"489bcfb86580b123547338c91db0eff2\" data-index=\"3\" style=\"float: none; margin:3px 0 3px 0; text-align:center;\">\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\"\r\n     style=\"display:block\"\r\n     data-ad-format=\"autorelaxed\"\r\n     data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6769524711517462\"\r\n     data-ad-slot=\"2473600074\"><\/ins>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"font-size: 0px; height: 