akthrough from Dev.D (2009). Due to his contribution to films and cinema, the government of France awarded him\u00a0the\u00a0Ordre des Arts et des Lettres\u00a0(Knight of the Order of\u00a0Arts and letters) in 2013. Wiki\/Biography Anurag Kashyap was born on 10 September 1972 (Age: 48 years old, as of 2020) in Gorakhpur, Uttar Pradesh, India. His father, Prakash Singh was a Chief Engineer of Uttar Pradesh Power Corporation Limited. <\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":18,"featured_media":22738,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[3],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/22737"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/18"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=22737"}],"version-history":[{"count":18,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/22737\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":218258,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/22737\/revisions\/218258"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/22738"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=22737"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=22737"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=22737"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}